  "detailed_description": "<h1>Student Project</h1><p><br>Viking Hiking is a student project made by a passionate team from Breda University of Applied Sciences. We worked on this project for about four months. <br><br>It would not have been the same if we had not had your support during development. We are very curious to get your opinions and feedback so join our Discord and become part of our Community!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/7f1a106cf86319491c3b4741915e3fd3.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=65 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/fe585a5fc76412a15d42ea6987f6c36a.poster.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/fe585a5fc76412a15d42ea6987f6c36a.webm?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/fe585a5fc76412a15d42ea6987f6c36a.mp4?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Viking Hiking is a 3D Platformer featuring a buff viking called 'Bøf, son of Tøf', on a quest to reach Valhalla. Bøf carries a magic horn that he uses in an 'unconventional' way. Jump, dash and vault with the horn to overcome obstacles and explore the environment.  <br>Are you ready to prove yourself worthy in the eyes of the gods? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/04771de43e61540ca0325a78b4f7bdbe.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=65 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/d8d70e0d96e98a98add263ec1e7c1806.poster.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/d8d70e0d96e98a98add263ec1e7c1806.webm?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/d8d70e0d96e98a98add263ec1e7c1806.mp4?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bøf can freely explore an entire island. It is up to you to decide which path to take to collect the necessary runes. <br>Confront numerous platforming trials and devise your own way to conquer them. <br>Let yourself be carried away by the beauty of this lush but challenging island!<br>An epic journey awaits you adventurer",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/7f1a106cf86319491c3b4741915e3fd3.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=65 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/fe585a5fc76412a15d42ea6987f6c36a.poster.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/fe585a5fc76412a15d42ea6987f6c36a.webm?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/fe585a5fc76412a15d42ea6987f6c36a.mp4?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Viking Hiking is a 3D Platformer featuring a buff viking called 'Bøf, son of Tøf', on a quest to reach Valhalla. Bøf carries a magic horn that he uses in an 'unconventional' way. Jump, dash and vault with the horn to overcome obstacles and explore the environment.  <br>Are you ready to prove yourself worthy in the eyes of the gods? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/04771de43e61540ca0325a78b4f7bdbe.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=65 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/d8d70e0d96e98a98add263ec1e7c1806.poster.avif?t=1699175307\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/d8d70e0d96e98a98add263ec1e7c1806.webm?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497390/extras/d8d70e0d96e98a98add263ec1e7c1806.mp4?t=1699175307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bøf can freely explore an entire island. It is up to you to decide which path to take to collect the necessary runes. <br>Confront numerous platforming trials and devise your own way to conquer them. <br>Let yourself be carried away by the beauty of this lush but challenging island!<br>An epic journey awaits you adventurer",
